data.description: APPOINTMENT ONLY OPEN HOUSE. February  19th and 20th. Must schedule with Agent directly to get your timeslot.   Contact Listing Agent or your Real Estate Agent.    Welcome to this beautiful home equipped with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, an oversized living room, and a whole lot more! This home is situated on almost 5 stunning acres of useable land. The master oasis has a huge master bathroom with a jetted tub, shower, and the oasis features a wall of closets. The back of the property has fenced pens and a gated 2 acres beyond that for animals to roam. This gorgeous home has everything you want for a growing family. Schedule you're showing today!
